  "2026-05-23T22:25:11.011Z",codex,"The incorrect v2026.05.23-7 release remains published as historical evidence,but the corrective release will be v2026.05.24."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T22:24:21.413Z",codex,Use an explicit RELEASE_TIMEZONE environment variable rather than relying on runner default timezone.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T22:24:21.413Z",codex,Date-based release workflows must define the business timezone or near-midnight dispatches can publish under the wrong date.
