close_reason: Release workflow timezone fixed and verified
body: "Observed at 2026-05-24 00:23 Europe/Vienna while UTC was still 2026-05-23 22:23. The workflow line release_date=\"2026.05.23\" caused the corrective production-readiness release to publish as v2026.05.23-7 instead of v2026.05.24."
